reqBody.prompt: Highly detailed anime-style image of a young, elegant college instructor with sandals, short brown hair, brown eyes, fox ears, and a red fox tail. She has medium breasts and wears simple, sleeveless clothing. She stands with her feet together, legs shoulder-width apart, and arms held straight out to the sides. She looks directly at the viewer with a neutral expression. The image should use an orthographic projection, a limited color palette, and a deep black background.
